        "setup": "Sign in at [Tango](https://tango.makegov.com/accounts/login/) and create an API key from your Tango account/API key area. The docs' easiest path is the quick start on [govcon.dev](https://govcon.dev/) / [Quick start](https://docs.makegov.com/getting-started/quick-start/), which begins with getting your API key. Use it as `Authorization: Api-Key <key>` for the HTTP API; the MCP docs and blog also say agents can authenticate with your API key.",
